name: .NET Micro Framework Interpreter
tagline: Interpreter, Base Cass Libraries and native code porting layer for the .NET Micro Framework
body:
### Welcome to the .NET Micro Framework interpreter.
This repository contains the source code to the .NET Micro Framework interpreter engine, Base Class Libraries and the native code Platform and Hardware Abstraction Layers (PAL/HAL) v4.4 and later. (For v4.3 and earlier see the [.NET Micro Framework CodePlex site](http://netmf.codeplex.com) )

### Releases
This is where we will post links to officially released binaries for the SDK. At present there aren't any as v4.4 is still under development. However, the v4.3 installers are available from the [.NET Micro Framework CodePlex site](http://netmf.codeplex.com/releases/view/611040) 

### Developer Builds
This is where we will post links to the latest developer builds. There aren't any yet as we haven't set up our automated build system to connect to GitHub yet. Once we do we'll have regular builds here for partner and early adopter testing and validation.
